The reason there are not more seeders is that this is an original file.  Hence, it has to start from one seed.  As I write this, there are 40 seeders.

I am open to suggestions as to how to more rapidly seed feeds with the bandwidth I have.  Until I learn of a different way, I will make the best use of my bandwidth that I can, and limit the number of files I am seeding at a time.
The movie itself is odd/strange. The ending seems slightly abrupt and makes no sense at all, but maybe that's just me..

This movie is one of the best movies ever! It's one of the few movies that are really thrilling. And the end is good too!
Thanx for sharing!

To explain the end of the film would ruin the film for other peeps.  The ultimate explanation, and the most honest one, is that the end means whatever you think it means.

-DogNo7

You're right dogno, I've seen the movie once and it kinda blew me away. I didn't exactly knew what the end was about, but it didn't matter much to me. I think the whole movie was great, building up the excitement and all the mysterious stuff. 

A really nice movie that lets you thinking when the end credits are rolling.
